<br>
Something touches your knee and you jump.  A cat is standing there looking up at you.  But this cat is different too somehow with an amazing intelligence in its eyes.<br>
<br>
&quot;Hello,&quot; is says in perfect speech.<br>
<br>
Your eyes open wide and you watch as it jumps and mid jump turns into a mouse to land on your hand.  It runs up your sleeve and next to your ear which would have tickled you if you hadn't been so startled.<br>
<br>
&quot;What are you?&quot; you demand.<br>
<br>
&quot;Why I am your soul, or as they down there would call me your daemon.&quot;</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
